                            Chao Mao Bird Staff, expert in Chao Mao Bird with experienced of 3 years.
                        </p>
                        <div class="team__socials">
                            <a href="https://github.com/Echo2craft" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                        </div>
